{"id":232681682,"title":"如果愛是無私，那我們要如何愛自己？","content":"https://i.imgur.com/aRe4ae9.jpg\n\n這個世界總是矛盾的，一面告訴你要先愛自己才能愛別人，另一面又告訴你愛是無私的奉獻，彷彿忘記奉獻本身就是犧牲自己的行為。\n\n最後就跟Hebe唱的一樣，怎麼了這世界每個人都愛別人。\n\n因此我認為愛，是理解的過程。誕生於想要了解被你愛著的受體的想法，存在於渴望被了解的同時也了解著對方，毀滅於不再溝通。\n\n愛自己沒那麼複雜，花時間傾聽自己內心的聲音足矣。\n-\n喜歡可以追蹤我的IG\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/B6BNvvonhn8/?igshid=1xdux8x53m066","excerpt":"這個世界總是矛盾的，一面告訴你要先愛自己才能愛別人，另一面又告訴你愛是無私的奉獻，彷彿忘記奉獻本身就是犧牲自己的行為。最後就跟Hebe唱的一樣，怎麼了這世界每個人都愛別人。因此我認為愛，是理解的過程。","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-13T16:28:55.660Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-14T20:29:55.371Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["愛自己","創作","文字","詩文","短文"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"冬片微微","department":"anothert","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":13}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/aRe4ae9.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"7780c664-c92f-4aca-9c2b-8a751834f3af","url":"https://i.imgur.com/aRe4ae9l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/aRe4ae9l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/aRe4ae9l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-13T16:28:55.660Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-14T20:29:55.371Z"},{"id":"7780c664-c92f-4aca-9c2b-8a751834f3af","url":"https://i.imgur.com/aRe4ae9.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/aRe4ae9","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/aRe4ae9l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-13T16:28:55.660Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-14T20:29:55.371Z"}],"postAvatar":""}